'''馬贊德蘭省'''（{{lang-fa|استان مازندران|Ostān-e Māzandarān}} {{pronunciation|Mazandaran.ogg}}，{{lang-mzn|مازرون|Māzerun}}）是位於[[裏海|裏海]]南岸的[[伊朗省份|伊朗省份]]，毗鄰[[伊朗|伊朗]]中央北邊的[[厄爾布爾士山脈|厄爾布爾士山脈]]。<ref name="NamesNote">Based on Maz or Mazan Term: {{lang-mzn|مازرون}} ''Māzerūn'', {{lang-fa|مازندران}}, {{lang-ru|Мазендеран}}.<br/>Based on Tapur Term: {{lang-en|Tapuria}}, {{lang-ar|طبرستان}} ''Ṭabaristan'', from [[Middle_Persian|Middle Persian]] ''Tapuristān''<br/>[[Mazandarani_people|Mazandarani]]: Tapurana. (not prevalent)<br/>[[Ancient_Greek|Ancient Greek]]: [[Hyrcania|Hyrcania]] came from local name Vergana (Persian [[Gorgan|Gorgan]]), [[Caspia|Caspia]] from local name Kaspi, See [[Caspian_Sea|Caspian Sea]].</ref>

馬贊達蘭省是伊朗人口最稠密的省份之一<ref>Statistical Centre, [[Government_of_Iran|Government of Iran]]. See: [http://www.sci.org.ir/Englishold/SEL/F1/S1_4S.htm "General Characteristics of Ostans according to their administrative divisions at the end of 1383 (2005 CE)"] {{dead link|date=March 2017|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}} , [http://www.sci.org.ir/Englishold/SEL/j-shvro-84.htm "Population estimation by urban and rural areas, 2005"]{{Dead link|date=August 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，擁有多樣天然資源，尤其是大量的[[石油|石油]]和[[天然氣|天然氣]]蘊藏。<ref name="umz:mazanderan">[http://www.umz.ac.ir/en/about_mazandaran.asp University of Mazanderan]  {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003211510/http://www.umz.ac.ir/en/about_mazandaran.asp |date=October 3, 2008 }}</ref>這個省四個最大的城市為[[薩里市|薩里市]]，[[阿莫勒|阿莫勒]]，{{link-en|努爾|Nur}}，和[[通卡邦|通卡邦]]。<ref name="Census2006">Census Results, 2006: Sari: 490.830,  Babel: 464.535,  Amel: 343.747, Shahi: 293.721. <br/>[http://www.sci.org.ir/portal/faces/public/census85/census85.natayej/census85.informationfile Iranian 2006 Census Website, Information File] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070601034554/http://www.sci.org.ir/portal/faces/public/census85/census85.natayej/census85.informationfile |date=June 1, 2007 }} (in Persian)</ref>建省時間在公元1937年。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.irib.ir/radioculture/iran/tourism/item/169927-natural-attractions-of-mazandaran |title=Natural attractions of Mazandaran in IRIB |access-date=2016-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306155311/http://english.irib.ir/radioculture/iran/tourism/item/169927-natural-attractions-of-mazandaran |archive-date=2017-03-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref>

這個省有多樣的自然特徵，有平原、[[大草原|大草原]]、森林、和[[雨林|雨林]]<ref>Springer Netherlands; July 10, 2005; [https://doi.org/10.1007%2FBF01897195 Contributions to the knowledge of the useful plants and plant raw materials of Iran]; {{ISSN|0921-9668}}</ref>，從裏海海灘延伸到崎嶇，且有厄爾布爾士山脈受積雪覆蓋的山脊<ref>[http://www.aftab.ir/english/iran/mpr.php Mazandaran, Geography & History] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228070330/http://www.aftab.ir/english/iran/mpr.php |date=February 28, 2008 }}</ref>，厄爾布爾士山脈擁有亞洲高度首屈一指的火山-[[德馬峰|德馬峰]]。<ref name="britannica:elburz">[http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9032241/Elburz-Mountains ''Encyclopædia Britannica'', Entry for Elburz] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080503005454/http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9032241/Elburz-Mountains |date=May 3, 2008 }}</ref>

馬贊德蘭省是養殖魚類的主要省份，<ref name="Briancoad">[http://www.briancoad.com/Introduction/caspianseabasin.htm Freshwater Fishes of Iran] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172431/http://www.briancoad.com/Introduction/caspianseabasin.htm |date=March 3, 2016 }}; Revised: 12 July 2007</ref>[[水產養殖|水產養殖]]對於當地以傳統農業為主的經濟活動，提供有重要的補充。<ref name="britannica:mazanderan">{{Cite web |url=http://www.britannica.com/ebc/article-9051626 |title=''Encyclopædia Britannica'', Entry for Mazandaran |accessdate=2020-03-01 |archive-date=2007-06-24 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20070624083706/http://www.britannica.com/ebc/article-9051626 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>由於伊朗各地的人都喜歡到這個省份旅遊，所以[[旅遊業|旅遊業]]也是另一對當地經濟提供重要貢獻的來源。<ref>[http://www.irexpert.ir/Webforms/News/NewNewsDetail.aspx?EvID=20462] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20070626122412/http://www.irexpert.ir/Webforms/News/NewNewsDetail.aspx?EvID=20462 |date=2007-06-26 }} (Persian)</ref>馬贊德蘭省也是一個快速發展的[[生物技術|生物技術]]中心。<ref name="umz:mazanderan" />

== 行政劃分==
全省面積23,842平方公里。<ref>http://www.sci.org.ir/content/userfiles/_sci_en/sci_en/sel/year85/f1/CS_01_4.HTM{{dead link|date=November 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>省會為[[薩里市|薩里市]]。

馬贊德蘭省有20個[[縣_(伊朗)|縣]]（[[波斯語|波斯語]]稱為shahrestan）。除{{link-en|薩瓦庫縣|Savadkooh county}}以外，省內其他的縣名都用當地行政中心之名來命名。

這20個縣中，15個縣的[[波斯語|波斯語]]名稱、[[英語|英語]]譯名及[[漢語|漢語]]譯名分別如下：
